        |       |       |       |       |       | 3.(no reply)
        |       |       |       |       |       |
                    
        1. Send Router Advertisement. (HA0 -> HA0_allnode_multi)
        2. Send Neighbor Solicitation (DAD). (Unspecified -> NUT0)
        3. (no reply)
                    
</PRE>

=end html

=head1 TEST PROCEDURE

=begin html
<PRE>
                    
      LFN0    NUT0     HA0      R1      R2     CN0
        |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | <---- |       |       |       | 1.Neighbor Solicitation (DAD)
        |       | ----> |       |       |       | 2.Neighbor Advertisement (*1)
        |       |       |       |       |       |
                    
        1. Send Neighbor Solicitation (DAD). (Unspecified -> NUT0)
        2. Receive Neighbor Advertisement. (NUT0 -> HA0)
                    
    Focus Packet Format:
        1. Neighbor Solicitation (DAD) Data is:
            IPv6 header
                source          = 0::0,
                destination     = solicited node multicast address)
            ICMPv6 header
              Neighbor Solicitation
                target address  = egress link-local address of nut0
                    
        2.Neighbor Advertisement is:
            IPv6 header
                source          = egress link-local or global address of nut0
                destination     = allnode multicast address
            ICMPv6 header
              Neighbor Advertisement
                R               = 1
                S               = 1
                target address = egress link-local address of nut0
              Target link-layer address option
                link-layer address = nut0
</PRE>

=end html

